You should go home.

138
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:42,650
我正要回去
I am going.

139
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:45,980
我只是得安排一个替补保镖
I just need to make arrangements for a replacement bodyguard.

140
00:07:46,090 --> 00:07:48,430
你打流感疫苗了吗  我从没打过
Did you get the flu shot? Personally, I never do.

141
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,260
