I know that I should.

142
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:51,870
可我  我对针头很恐惧
I just, I have this thing about needles.

143
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,240
对尖的东西都恐惧
All pointy things, really.

144
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,530
这很讽刺  想想我们跟谁共事
Which is ironic, considering who we work with.

145
00:07:55,530 --> 00:07:57,750
对  不是流感  费利西蒂  更像是
Yeah, it's not the flu, Felicity, it's more like...

146
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,590
狄格
Dig!

147
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:02,590
有人吗
Hello?

148
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,430
你在这里吗
Are you here?

149
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:08,250
在这里  在那里
Here...there...

150
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:10,010
在任何地方
Everywhere.

151
