我把他的血样给了公司里的一个化学家
I sent a sample of his blood to a chemist I know at QC.

176
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,890
他欠我人情  说来话长
The guy owes me a favor. Long story,

177
00:09:24,890 --> 00:09:26,170
