I fixed his parking ticket.

178
00:09:26,170 --> 00:09:28,050
其实也不是很长
Huh. I guess it's not that long.

179
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:30,160
费利西蒂  血样
Felicity. The blood sample.

180
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:33,680
对  迷魂检测的结果  显示阳性
Yeah. It came back positive-- for trace amounts of Vertigo.

181
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,060
我从没用过迷魂
I never used Vertigo before in my life.

182
00:09:35,060 --> 00:09:36,710
你肯定是接触到了
You were exposed to it somehow.

183
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,100
迷魂又出现了吗
Vertigo's in play again?

184
